          Xilinx Arty SoC based on LiteX

[> Getting started
1. Install Python3 and your vendor's software

2. Obtain LiteX and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litex --recursive
  cd litex
  python3 setup.py install
  cd ..

3. Obtain LiteEth and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/liteeth
  cd liteeth
  python3 setup.py install
  cd ..

4. Obtain LiteScope and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litescope
  cd litescope
  python3 setup.py install
  cd ..

5. Build the gateware and software:
  goto gateware
  BaseSoC:
    python3 arty_base.py --build --load
  BaseSoC with ethernet:
    python3 arty_base.py --with-ethernet --build --load
  EtherboneSoC:
    python3 arty_etherbone.py --build --load

[> Status:
BaseSoC / MiniSoC validated (DDR3 and SPI still missing).
EtherboneSoC validated.

